DirectionalFilter
public static enum DirectionalFilter.Type
extends java.lang.Enum<DirectionalFilter.Type>
Specifies how to combine the different orientations: min or max. Use MIN to enhance dark thin of the results, and MAX to enhance bright thin structures.
